body:
@vandernorth

I'm trying to figure out what the intended behavior of `processImports` is. It doesn't seem to be documented here: http://lesscss.org/usage/, and [in the code](https://github.com/less/less.js/blob/master/packages/less/src/less/contexts.js#L32), it is sort of vague as to the output implications. 

So, can you point to where you found this option documented, how you are you using it, and how you expect this to function in regards to output?
